 ## @keystone-next/keystone@19.0.0

### Major Changes

-   [#5806](https://github.com/keystonejs/keystone/pull/5806) [`0eadba2ba`](https://github.com/keystonejs/keystone/commit/0eadba2badb13fc6a17f7e525d429494ca953481) Thanks [@list({]\(, [@list({]\( - Removed `withItemData` in favour of a `sessionData` option to the `createAuth()` function.

    Previously, `withItemData` would be used to wrap the `config.session` argument:

    ```typescript
    import { config, createSchema, list } from '@keystone-next/keystone/schema';
    import { statelessSessions, withAuthData } from '@keystone-next/keystone/session';
    import { text, password, checkbox } from '@keystone-next/fields';
